==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{italbrac|Australian, New Zealand and British taboo slang}} A person who [[wank]]s.
# {{italbrac|Australian, New Zealand and British taboo slang}} An idiot. A stupid, annoying or ineffectual person.
# {{italbrac|Australian, New Zealand and British taboo slang}} Someone who shows off too much.  Someone who loves himself.

====Usage notes====
This term has been used openly in British and Australian film and television productions in reference to the second term of use (ie; an idiot in the perjorative sense.) The term has been picked up and used extensivly by [[American television]] producers and writers who use it freely to mean a simpleton, not , apparently, realising it is taboo slang and not appropriate to the use or context - much less the target audience- to which it is applied.

